{"type":"text","timestamp":1781151328055,"sessionID":"ses_14b1d6f10ffe46iC74jznEPrC4","part":{"id":"prt_eb4e46365001lz9nYp02c6If0X","messageID":"msg_eb4e40411001V5a7EIycizdHRV","sessionID":"ses_14b1d6f10ffe46iC74jznEPrC4","type":"text","text":"The review found one active correctness issue: the repair job atomically replaces the shard file while the live SQLite connection remains attached to the old shard handle, so the current process can stay on an empty/stale `active_vec` after rebuild. I am writing the lineage artifacts with a conditional verdict.","time":{"start":1781151327077,"end":1781151328050},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_01f1e8c30fd1d5f8016a2a365f12e88191975be5bb40fd1245","phase":"commentary"}}}}
